reviews:
We hired Matt as our wedding photographer.
I really don’t like having my photo taken but he made me feel really comfortable and relaxed.
He fit in so well with everyone, our guests all loved him and commented on how nice he is.
He is sooo affordable and his photos are always amazing!
If you are considering hiring him I would highly recommend, you most certainly will not regret it.

We booked Matt for our wedding in May this year. We couldn’t recommend him enough to anybody considering booking him for an event. Within minutes of him arriving at my house, I knew we were in good hands. He slotted in perfectly with our friends and family, which was lovely, and he made our photos feel natural and effortless. We are so pleased with the few preview pictures he has sent us so far. Thank you, Matt 💯!

TL;DR:
Matt's photography is fantastic (and he's pretty great too) our photos turned out better than we could ever have imagined. Booking Matt was one of the best decisions we made for our wedding!

The long version:
Photography and preserving memories are incredibly important to us, that is why for our wedding one of first suppliers to book was our photographer.

Despite being incredibly fussy, we spoke to a grand total of one photographer, we were sold straight away. That was Matt.

You can already see from Matt's previous images, the absolute quality of his work. We initially asked for a meeting because of a shot he took at a previous wedding at our venue, but the fact that he is a funny, engaging and professional helped make our decision to pick him an easy one.

On the day itself, Matt put everyone at ease, managing to take natural unobtrusive shots yet capturing everything we wanted from the day. Several of our guests commented on how friendly he was.

With the weather not on our side, he already had contingency plans in place for where to take some of our more formal shots something which we didn't even have time to consider.

Communication with Matt has was excellent, making sure that we were updated updated every step of the way, picking up the little things during our planning stages and even after the weeding itself.

With the pictures now in our possession, we're over the moon at how well they have turned out, we can't wait to try and narrow them down to get them into an album (it will be difficult as all of them are incredible!)

On a separate note, we've actually used Matt for his photography skills on three occasions now, and will see if he's available for any future events too!

Thank you again Matt for all of your help capturing our journey together, you're the best.

Matt was the photographer for my wedding (August 2021) and he was amazing. Friendly, helped out with the running of day, and took the most beautiful pictures. I am so pleased we chose Matt to photograph our day. Thoroughly recommended

We cannot recommend Matts services enough! He was absolutely brilliant on our wedding day from start to finish. Very professional, we met a few times before the wedding, got a great feel of exactly what we were after. Made us feel completely relaxed.On the day he was great at blending in with the guests,made us feel so comfortable being photographed and was amazing at capturing the kids too. He was a great help throughout the day and was happy to do any adhoc photographs we requested. The pictures we received are beautiful! Definitely recommend. Thanks again Matt!

We first met Matt when he was the photographer at a friend’s wedding and thought he was great; friendly but assertive. So as soon as we started to plan our wedding we booked him up straight away. We couldn’t have asked for a better photographer to capture our day. He was professional, approachable and made everyone feel so comfortable throughout. Would highly recommend!

My maid of honour worked with Matt and after we met with him it was clear how passionate he was about photography and capturing special moments.  We had so look through his portfolio and booked him! With the booking we had an engagement shoot which I highly recomend as we got to know Matt, he got to know us, we were put at ease and the photos were amazing.  On the day of the wedding Matt was very much in the background and we weren't often aware of his presence.  He had great ideas on certain photos and everyone said what a great guy he is! He got wonderful photos of all our guests and really did a class job. We have no hesitation recommending him and will to our friends when they all get engaged. We will treasure our wedding photos.  Thank you Matt for recording our special day so well! I was so impatient waiting for the finished wedding photos as the engagement shoot was so good; sorry Matt! The presentation box and USB was great and we had the flexibility to print off what we wanted to use in our album and get plenty frames and even a canvas.

Matt was fantastic while doing our wedding day photography. Everyone was very impressed with his professionalism and liked that he introduced himself to our guests.
Everyone has loved the pictures he took. He caught some lovely moments during the ceremony and the more formal pictures afterwards are gorgeous. He has an eye for what to capture and took our beautiful scenery into account too, even getting our reflections in the lake!. We also loved the informal pictures he took throughout the day of our families and  friends. They have all been keen for copies of the photos! Matt captured the day perfectly!
Thank you

Matt was absolutely brilliant at our wedding, we couldn’t of asked for better photos they are perfect. The photos captured every part of our special day and are so natural which is exactly what we wanted.
Matt is very friendly and professional from the moment we met.
We had a few meetings to discuss ideas and he knew exactly how we wanted the photos to look. He has great ideas and it was easy to discuss my ideas of a few different photos I wanted.
He was fantastic on the day and helped me arrange everything. At times I didn’t even realise he was there.
Thank you Matt for being a fantastic photographer at our wedding- we love our photos memories that will last forever!
“A photo says a thousand words “  
We will 100% be recommending Matt!

Thank you again Matt
Mr & Mrs Snuggs x

Matt was recommended to us by our florist for our wedding photography, we instantly decided he was perfect as he is so easy to get on with, he's a really genuinely nice guy and is easy to feel comfortable around. On the wedding day he was fantastic, dealt well with me having a minor meltdown pre-ceremony, made all of our guests feel comfortable and a few have stated that they will be asking him to be their photographer.
He is not only happy to do the 'traditional' photos but will shoot silly mucking around ones and even took a few family photos of family groups who were guests at the wedding.

Cannot recommend him highly enough definitely feel choosing him was the best decision we made!
Thanks a million again Matt!
Mr & Mrs Killip

Best Decision Ever!!!
We are so happy to have found Matt! He has a wonderful way of making you feel relaxed on, quite possibly, the most stressful day of your life. I think this is because he approaches your Special Day as if it was his, giving the photos an extra personal touch. He is friendly and approachable, and he will guide you through your day. Matt captured some very precious moments, that we weren’t even able to process, so when it came to looking at the photos it was like reliving it all over again. Magic!!

What a lovely guy, great pictures and a good laugh. Nothing was too much trouble. Will be booking him for everything we can. Already recommended him to family members for their weddings as the photographs are amazing, helping us remember our special day with great shots.
Love Margesson photography, he is just such a nice friendly warm photographer and i would recommend him to anyone on their special day.
Matt is amazing and made us both feel so comfortable! Can not recommend enough
